{"tid":1992895,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黨衛軍進入IFC驅散 向最少兩人發出定額告票","createTime":"2020-04-28T11:52:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-28T12:17:59.000Z","uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3bcfccb57217aa5146905e75056672d08eb7762f","tid":1992895,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T11:52:05.000Z","msg":"有人發起在中環IFC集叫口號 警員進入商場驅散發告票<br />\n28.04.2020 19:36<br />\n<br />\n有人發起傍晚在中環國際金融中心商場「和你唱」，約幾十人在商場各層聚集，高叫反修例及針對警隊口號，在商場中庭，有人展示反修例標語，大批警員晚上多次進入商場驅散，一度在商場中庭拉起封鎖線，指參與的人違反「限聚令」，要求他們散去，警告後向最少兩人發出定額罰款2000元的告票。期間多間商店落閘。<br />\n<br />\n有區議員與警方理論，要求警方解釋進入商場的理據。現場警員指，是收到有人報警而進入商場。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1283984&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1283984%26csid%3D261_341&d=mbsn9%2Fi9gU9wZYjOUdyYPlwLDRbgpiba54y0vEBNjMo%3D&h=6f8310a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1283984&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"70708c073fa83602822129b228c316b13d08d920","tid":1992895,"uid":55162,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T11:53:48.000Z","msg":"扮咩撚野有人報警<br />\nLunch time已經見到幾架警車係中環"},{"pid":"6dba7f34623319074e4588efb54187b970c6c3c5","tid":1992895,"uid":89349,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T11:56:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZrEZ1hS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZrEZ1hS.png&h=8e451fd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac